{"tid":1296082,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支持將部份屯門公園劃為紅燈區","createTime":"2019-07-08T08:55:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T15:07:06.000Z","uid":265268,"like":1632,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":122,"replies":[{"pid":"5cc198596632894150e193480fe7fa58b222e3f1","tid":1296082,"uid":265268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T08:55:58.000Z","msg":"如果市民自發光復失敗<br />\n既然大媽同老友記有供求關係, 地區組織又需要搵食<br />\n不如索性倡議設立 <span style=\"color: red;\">屯門公園紅燈區</span> (如圖)<br />\n<br />\n香港首創<br />\n可參考荷蘭阿姆斯特丹, 配合發牌制度<br />\n四周加設隔音屏障, 以免影響鄰近親子區<br />\n由旅發局 / 中旅社加以推廣, 成為世界級旅遊景點<br />\n有管制, 有庫房收入, 又照顧到各方需要<br />\n我覺得有得做喎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0LugXXZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0LugXXZ.jpg&h=bbf667bf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e04010b4e4f56698d6890ca17c2e7cc09717395d","tid":1296082,"uid":12558,"like":33,"dislike":1,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T09:04:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8031ed689e202999d5924f8e2e32331cf56d8066","tid":1296082,"uid":17641,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T09:07:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3bb15aa01638be4762a1bedfe274dfbc904b79e","tid":1296082,"uid":265268,"like":363,"dislike":3,"score":360,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T09:13:59.000Z","msg":"園區內景色 (設計圖片)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bU3EV0D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbU3EV0D.jpg&h=dfecd0ad&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KhrSwyY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKhrSwyY.jpg&h=241ed63b&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OdWGpTZ.